data.chText: 他不会赞同凯利做的事。
data.enText: He would doubtless disapprove of what Kelly was doing.

value.def: If you say that something is doubtless the case, you mean that you think it is probably or almost certainly the case.

example.ex: He will doubtless try and persuade his colleagues to change their minds...
example.tran: 他很可能会试图说服同事们改变主意。

example.ex: Doubtless he was justified in some of his criticism of the media...
example.tran: 他对媒体的一些批评性言论无疑是合乎情理的。

example.ex: She took off her shoes, doubtless because her feet hurt.
example.tran: 她脱掉了鞋子，大概是因为脚疼。
